   <#
.SYNOPSIS
    This PowerShell script the network selection user interface (UI) must not be displayed on the logon screen.

.NOTES
    Author          : Enioluwa akinwande
    LinkedIn        : https://www.linkedin.com/in/enioluwa-akinwande-a5b597254/
